    "headline": "TPG Refocuses On Clean Energy With Intersect Exit And IPX Power Launch",
    "summary": "TPG Rise Climate has completed the sale of its stake in solar and storage platform Intersect to Google. Following the transaction, TPG is spinning out a new independent power company called IPX Power. TPG will remain a majority backer of IPX Power, focused on clean energy infrastructure. TPG, listed as NasdaqGS:TPG, is reshaping its climate focused portfolio through the Intersect sale and the launch of IPX Power. The move comes with the shares at $40.68 and a 62.6% return over 3 years,...",
